Description: A comprehensive R/Shiny platform for RNA-seq, microarray and
    single-cell cluster-derived pseudobulk downstream analysis. Supports
    differential expression (limma-voom, edgeR), functional enrichment
    (KEGG, GO, GSEA), pathway and TF activity inference (CollecTRI, DoRothEA
    with A-D confidence levels, TF family enrichment via Fisher exact test),
    and AI-powered biological interpretation.
